---

## ğŸŒŸ Overview

The **Brain Tumor Detector & Classifier** leverages the power of deep learning to assist in the preliminary classification of brain MRI scans. Using a fine-tuned VGG16 convolutional neural network, the system can identify and classify four distinct categories:

- ğŸ”´ **Glioma Tumor**
- ğŸŸ£ **Meningioma Tumor**
- ğŸŸ¡ **Pituitary Tumor**
- ğŸŸ¢ **No Tumor Detected**

Built with Flask and TensorFlow, this application provides an intuitive web interface for researchers and students to explore medical image classification.

---

## âœ¨ Features

- ğŸ¯ **Multi-Class Classification** - Accurately classifies MRI scans into 4 distinct categories
- ğŸ“Š **Confidence Scoring** - Displays prediction confidence as a percentage
- ğŸ“‹ **Medical Summaries** - Provides educational information about each tumor type
- ğŸ‘¨â€âš•ï¸ **Specialist Recommendations** - Suggests appropriate medical specialists for consultation
- ğŸ¨ **Clean UI/UX** - Modern, responsive web interface for easy interaction
- âš¡ **Fast Predictions** - Quick inference time for real-time classification

